{
  "id": "adv_bond_kan_01_05",
  "title": "kana5",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――番組撮影中　化粧直し",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― During filming‚ touching up makeup",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.1666666627
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あ～～～～最悪最悪最悪っ！　なんでスタジオ入って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Argh~~ Worst‚ worst‚ WORST! Not even ten seconds",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.0666667502,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "十秒でこんなビショビショにされなきゃなんだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "into the studio and I’m already soaking wet!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.3333334168
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "ドッキリ仕掛けられた挙句、「化粧直しは十分でお願い\nします」だと？　それも自分で？　舐めやがって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "On top of the prank‚ they say \"Touch up your makeup\nin ten minutes\"? And do it myself? They're mocking me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.3333334168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.9333334168
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "水風呂に突き落とすドッキリってのも古過ぎるし\nリズノワの筋肉バカは手加減知らな過ぎ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pushing someone into a cold bath is such an old prank‚\nand that muscle idiot from LizNoir has no restraint!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.9333334168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "突き落とす時の力の強さにスタッフ全員ドン引き\nだったじゃん。あいつバカなの？　バカなんだろうな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even the staff were horrified by how hard she pushed me.\nIs she stupid? She definitely is.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.8000000835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はぁ～、マージであの筋肉バカ、覚えとけよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh~ Seriously‚ that muscle idiot‚ you just wait.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.4333334168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.4333334168
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "二度とkanaに舐めた態度とれねえようにしてやる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll make sure she never looks down on Kana again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2899.9999999999986
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.0000000835
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "失礼します！！！！！！\n先ほどは大変申し訳ございませんでしたぁぁぁぁっ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "EXCUSE ME!!!!!!\nI AM TERRIBLY SORRY FOR WHAT HAPPENED EARLIER!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.0000000835,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 233.3332498000047
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.0855422548
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.1999975404
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "うるせぇ～～～～！　勝手に人の楽屋入ってきて\n土下座すんな！　化粧直しの邪魔、出ていって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "SHUT UP~~! Don’t just barge in here\nand prostrate yourself! You're in my way‚ get out!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.1999975404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.3333308738
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "すみません！　すみません！　すっぴん……\nはっ！？　見てしまってすみません！！！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry! I'm sorry! Your bare face…\nAh!? I'M SORRY FOR LOOKING!!!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.3333308738,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.1000000836
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "うっぜ～！　じろじろ見られんのもムカつくけど\n見ちゃいけないものみたいに目を逸らされんのも腹立つ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re so annoying! Staring is aggravating enough‚\nbut looking away like I’m a freak is even worse.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.1000000836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "わ、私は一体どうすれば！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wh-What am I supposed to do then!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.3000000836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.3000000836
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……チラッ……チラチラッ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… Glance… peek‚ peek…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.1000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "ああ？　煽ってんのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Are you mocking me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.4666667503,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.4666667503
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "い、いえいえいえ！　本当に真剣に謝りに来たんです\nこんなにうまく引っかかると思ってなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-No‚ no‚ no! I really came here to apologize sincerely.\nI just didn’t expect you to fall for it so perfectly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.4000000836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.4000000836
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "煽ってんなぁ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re definitely mocking me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.5333288393,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.5333288393
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.799995506
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "あああああああ煽ってないです！\nすみません、すみません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aaaaaaah‚ I'm not mocking you!\nI'm sorry‚ I'm sorry!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.799995506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そもそもなんであんたがkanaにドッキリなんか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you even the one pranking Kana",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.8333288393,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.8333288393
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "仕掛けてくるわけ？　こころならまだ分かるけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "in the first place? If it were Kokoro‚ I’d get it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.7666620892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、どうせこころにそそのかされたとか\n騙されたとかそんな感じでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I bet Kokoro either coaxed you\nor tricked you into doing it‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.6333288393,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.6333288393
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "いえ！　違います！　百パーセント私の意志です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No! Not at all! This was 100% my own decision!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.899995506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.899995506
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "違うんかい！　それならなおさらなんでkanaに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not her?! Then even more so‚ why would you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.9333288393,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.9333288393
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "ドッキリ仕掛けるんだよ！　意味分かんねーよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "prank ME! That makes no sense at all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.1999954225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "実は番組の企画でドッキリの仕掛け人に選ばれてしまい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ the show chose me to be the prankster‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.0666621727,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.0666621727
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_05-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "誰に仕掛けようかと悩みに悩んだ末……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and after agonizing over who to target…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.8999954225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
